reviewText: A fun movie! Great music and girls too.
Reminds me of why I love movies! Unlike anything you will see anywhere else!

Wow. This movie takes you back to when you understood what movies were.  Messages.  Clear from someone with a vision.  If you like metal, you'll love this. No holds barred metal movie.  And pretty hilarious.
This movie is the metal bomb.
Amazing and funny film writer and actor!
